title: Sanctuary Records Sampler - Megadeth Ministry & Gravity Kill
description:
Sanctuary Records Sampler Audio Disc SANDJ-85529-2

01. Megadeth - In My Darkest Hour (Live)
02. Megadeth - Prince Of Darkness (Live)
03. Ministry - Filth Pig (Live)
04. Ministry - Stigmata (Live)
05. Gravity Kills - Love, Sex And Money
06. Gravity Kills - Personal Jesus (Acoustic)

EAC Secure Ripped, Lame 320k HQ MP3

NOTES:
Three tracks were unreleased at the time of sampler release.  Prince Of Darkness Live, Stigmata Live and Personal Jesus Acoustic were never released on the CD format before this sampler was released.  It is possible they have been re-released since, I don't know.  Sampler did not come with any artwork.  

Enjoy!
